# ── Dependencies ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never send node_modules to the Docker daemon — they are installed inside
# the image during the deps stage.
**/node_modules

# ── Build outputs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.next
**/dist
**/out

# ── Mobile app ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The web Docker image does not need any mobile source files.
mobile/

# ── Secrets — must NEVER be baked into the image ─────────────────────────────
# .env files are excluded globally. NEXT_PUBLIC_* values are passed exclusively
# as --build-arg entries from docker-compose (sourced from the root .env file).
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.production
!**/.env.example

# ── Version control ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore

# ── Editor and OS noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
